        <p>Provides amino acids (glycine, proline) that support hair follicle structure. Effective dose: 2.5-5g daily. A 2015 study showed increased hair strand diameter after 90 days. Note: all collagen is animal-derived.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="sun" size={22} /></div>
