      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="leaf" size={22} /></div>
        <h4>Folic Acid & B12</h4>
        <p>Support red blood cell production and oxygen delivery to the scalp. Deficiency can cause diffuse hair thinning. Particularly important for women on plant-based diets (B12) or those planning pregnancy (folate).</p>
